CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 12, 1946, pg. 21, reads: "Venison Party - Johnny Craig surprised his friends with a venison party at Crawford Grill No. 1 this week.  Johnny killed a deer on his last hunting trip, and this is the result of his marksmanship. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group, possibly including Johnny Craig, Robert E. "Pappy" Williams second on left, Johnny Black front right, and possibly Ann Baker in background, gathered around dining tables for venison party in Rumpus Room of Crawford Grill No. 1
